nl.tue.geometrycore.io.ipe

Class IPEReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.tue.geometrycore.io.BaseReader
      • nl.tue.geometrycore.io.ipe.IPEReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class IPEReader
extends BaseReader
    This class provides a reader for the IPE XML format. It can handle both files as well as selection code, allowing easy copy-pasting from IPE into Java. The applicable type is detected automatically.
